otropy in the IPC, which further modifies the PSF shapes.\nOur results are a first, critical step in determining the hardware and\ncharacterization requirements for the detectors used in the WFIRST survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2015 21:27:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2016 05:13:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-06"}
