osity and thickness ratios.\nThis analysis is relevant to applications such as solvent extraction in\nmicrochannels, in which a surface-active solute is transferred between fluids\nin parallel stratified flow. It is also applicable to the thermocapillary\nproblem of layered flow between heated plates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2015 23:43:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 16 Jan 2016 02:36:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2016 07:42:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-29"}
