 engineers interested in operads and wiring diagrams. Assuming no prior\nknowledge of categories, operads, and wiring diagrams, this monograph is\nself-contained and can be used as a supplement in a graduate course and for\nindependent study. There are over 100 graphical illustrations and a chapter\nwith a list of problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2015 00:39:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2016 19:39:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2017 14:53:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-19"}
