pheric activities of\nmagnetars are always stronger than those of normal pulsars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Dec 2015 15:32:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 06:19:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-03"}
